Module org.nasdanika.architecture.cloud.azure.compute
Package org.nasdanika.architecture.cloud.azure.compute

Interface ComputePackage.Literals

Enclosing interface:
ComputePackage
public static interface ComputePackage.Literals
Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each operation of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type
